This project uses different licenses depending on the type of content.

## License Structure

```
husamguk-game/
├── LICENSE                     # This file (License summary and guide)
└── husamguk/
    ├── LICENSES/
    │   ├── gpl-3.0.txt        # Full text of GPL-3.0
    │   └── cc-by-sa-4.0.txt   # Full text of CC-BY-SA-4.0
    ├── src/                    # Source code (GPL-3.0)
    ├── assets/                 # Game assets (CC-BY-SA-4.0)
    └── docs/                   # Documentation (CC-BY-SA-4.0)
```

## Applied Licenses

### 1. Source Code - GPL-3.0

All source code in this project is licensed under the **GNU General Public
License v3.0** (GPL-3.0).

**Applies to:**
- All source code in the `husamguk/src/` directory
- Game logic, scripts, and program files

**Full license text:** [husamguk/LICENSES/gpl-3.0.txt](husamguk/LICENSES/gpl-3.0.txt)

**Key permissions:**
- Commercial use
- Modification
- Distribution
- Patent use
- Private use

**Key conditions:**
- License and copyright notice required
- Source code must be disclosed
- Same license required for distribution
- State changes required


### 2. Assets and Documentation - CC-BY-SA-4.0

All game assets and documentation are licensed under **Creative Commons
Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International** (CC-BY-SA-4.0).

**Applies to:**
- All files in the `husamguk/assets/` directory (images, sounds, models, etc.)
- All documentation in the `husamguk/docs/` directory

**Full license text:** [husamguk/LICENSES/cc-by-sa-4.0.txt](husamguk/LICENSES/cc-by-sa-4.0.txt)

**Key permissions:**
- Commercial use
- Modification
- Distribution
- Private use

**Key conditions:**
- Attribution required
- License and copyright notice required
- Same license required for distribution (ShareAlike)
- State changes required


